{"tid":561410,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"年三十，介紹返【覆桌型利是封】畀大家！","createTime":"2018-02-15T03:49:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-16T20:26:37.000Z","uid":29314,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3cc7a09dc74103f9824118c12f3b08dd02ebbb49","tid":561410,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T03:49:14.000Z","msg":"聽日就係大年初一，黎緊呢幾日，無論你心入面幾唔願意都好，都要去拜年。<br />\n<br />\n個個去拜年，唔通個個都想去拜年咩？係果班一年先見一次面、食一次飯既親戚入面，實有幾個，因為唔同原因，自你懂事開始就好黑你憎。憎還憎，禮數都要足，除左送盒「嘉頓家庭雜餅」畀佢之外，仲可以點呢？西米今日介紹返兩款「覆桌型利是封」畀大家：<br />\n<br />\n第一款，係Dior出既狗年利是封。設計極簡約，紅色做底，只得一個「狗」字印係正中！仲唔係暗暗鬧人係狗？為左加強效果，梗係係個「狗」字上方寫埋乞人憎親戚個名啦。（親戚眾多，親疏有別，唔同人畀唔同銀碼，寫埋名唔怕撈亂！）<br />\n<br />\n第二款，係台灣總統府既出品。正中間印左一個燙銀既台幣一蚊既圖案。無論你係入面放二十、五十定一百蚊紙都好，加埋封面果「一蚊」都會變成單數，$21 / $51 / $101. . .寓意就係幫佢做定帛金！<br />\n<br />\n西米係度同大家拜個早年，祝各位新一年「小人退散」！恭喜恭喜！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/15/114830_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F15%2F114830_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=bcdb5604&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/15/114838_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F15%2F114838_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=92389397&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n西米Go fb &amp; ig同步連載：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/WestRiceGoo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FWestRiceGoo&d=X8FF1IDY7L640IgtqOALIxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=d3618d50\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/WestRiceGoo</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/westricegoo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fwestricegoo&d=X8FF1IDY7L640IgtqOALIxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=067a844e\" target=\"_blan